Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:02.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 喝點咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:05.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也不是特別的喜歡咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.14,0:00:08.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,但是我喜歡咖啡店裡的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:09.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:10.63,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.63,0:00:12.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,噢 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:16.40,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an2}{\1c&HA86C6F&}Re{\1c&HA9AB4B&}:{\1c&H7D60CC&}小{\1c&H4396E0&}劇場 {\1c&H000000&} 之三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:21.40,SignC,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}小{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}劇場{\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&HB8B80F&}❸{\1c&HBB878E&\3c&HFFFFFF&}主{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}人{\1c&HC2BA20&\3c&HFFFFFF&}和、他{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}的{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}女{\1c&HC2BA20&\3c&HFFFFFF&}仆們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.77,0:00:18.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,在這個情況...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,你真棒 異世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:23.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我夢想中的女僕咖啡館
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:24.75,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,雷姆雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人在說什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.47,0:00:28.13,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,大概腦子有點問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:29.27,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣主人也是很棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:35.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,雖然姐姐的反應讓我難以接受是一個女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:38.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不是對羅茲親 而是叫我主人 這種情況很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:43.03,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,主人 你能快點下單嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:44.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,我看一下菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:45.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆的暖暖蒸地瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:47.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,和整人蒸地瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有心情無常蒸地瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:50.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你這不是只有蒸地瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:52.18,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,價格不一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.18,0:00:54.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,根據價格殺必死也不一樣是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:55.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是女僕咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:57.65,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,根據地瓜的個數不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:00:59.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,普通 那個太普通了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒有嗎 女僕咖啡的殺必死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:06.33,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,我可以為了主人專門擺一個pose 一次500
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:08.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種就是這種
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:10.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,500塊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這個價格也有點普通
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但機會難得給我來一份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:15.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:17.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,這是嘲諷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:20.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候難道不是擺可愛的姿勢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.29,0:01:22.15,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐一直都很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:23.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,雷姆小姐雷姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能成為主人的同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:28.55,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我當然是主人的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:30.76,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,但是姐姐非常的棒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:32.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,那個 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:36.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候我覺得你應該對著我才對壓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:37.29,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,你說沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為女僕不看主人的確是有一些問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:41.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:43.61,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,那再給你特別弄一個姿勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:46.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,你這不是在鄙視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,講道理不應該尊敬我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.60,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐一直都很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:50.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,雷姆小姐雷姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要成為顧客的伙伴呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:55.84,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雷姆當然是顧客的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:58.01,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,但是姐姐非常的棒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:02:00.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,真是難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:03.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,作為女僕咖啡給我搞一些正經的殺必死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:05.54,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,確實是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:06.49,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:09.75,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,為了回應主人的希望 我可以給你一些女僕的殺必死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:11.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,就是要這樣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:14.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 有什麼殺必死呢 比如說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.31,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,比如...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:17.25,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,拳頭碎大桌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:19.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,你那不是女僕殺必死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:22.90,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,雷姆和姐姐所做的女僕殺必死是 雖然說沒什麼回頭客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:25.51,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,但也從來沒收到過什麼不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:30.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,OK 大概是對這些女僕不能抱有不滿這一點也預想到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:30.42,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(355,180)\1c&H1E1B76&}去死吧~     主人~♥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:31.32,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,
